        <abstract> 
<p>Krause altered the MS [of his essay on Erasmus Darwin] considerably before sending it to be translated. This is a common practice, but CD now regrets he did not state in his preface that the article had been modified. The translation had been arranged before SB’s book [<hi rend="italic">Evolution, old and new</hi>] was announced.</p> 
        </abstract>
